# Whoop API Configuration
# Get these from your Whoop Developer Dashboard: https://developer.whoop.com/
WHOOP_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
WHOOP_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here
WHOOP_REFRESH_TOKEN=your_refresh_token_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://developer.whoop.com/
# 2. Create an app and get your Client ID and Client Secret
# 3. Follow the OAuth flow to get a refresh token
# 4. Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values